00:09:39.909 --> 00:09:42.418
So it can be near or far.
 

00:09:42.418 --> 00:09:48.418
Okay, now let's look at these
two different,

00:09:48.418 --> 00:09:52.027
the 2D and the 3D pictures,
and look at the pattern of

00:09:52.027 --> 00:09:55.081
nodes,
the shape and the energy of the

00:09:55.081 --> 00:09:56.580
3d orbital.
 

00:09:56.580 --> 00:10:02.950
You see here that there are
diagonal nodes in this 3d

00:10:02.950 --> 00:10:04.029
orbital.
 

00:10:04.029 --> 00:10:04.980
Okay?
 

00:10:04.980 --> 00:10:08.690
So that's 3d.
 

00:10:08.690 --> 00:10:12.990
Let's look at this one.
 

00:10:12.990 --> 00:10:16.139
Now we still have those two
diagonal nodes.

00:10:16.139 --> 00:10:22.178
