00:10:27.080 --> 00:10:27.798
Okay?
 

00:10:27.798 --> 00:10:32.037
So the nodal surface -- bear in
mind that in one dimension a

00:10:32.037 --> 00:10:35.764
node is a point;
in two dimensions a node is a

