00:10:39.140 --> 00:10:39.730
Right?
 

00:10:39.730 --> 00:10:43.635
So we're slicing it and see an
intersection of the conical

00:10:43.635 --> 00:10:46.788
surface here,
but the actual node is a cone.

00:10:46.788 --> 00:10:50.793
Okay, but is that the only node
that you see in that picture on

00:10:50.793 --> 00:10:51.570
