00:43:55.809 --> 00:43:56.480
Okay?
 

00:43:56.480 --> 00:43:58.539
Wouldn't that be great?
 

00:43:58.539 --> 00:44:02.239
It's just paradise, right?
 

00:44:02.239 --> 00:44:05.440
Because if we had many
